[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "Repertoire Specific Rules"]
[Black "The Rooks"]
[Result "*"]

{ Let's talk about the rooks!   In the early opening phase, rooks typically don't play a significant role. However, castling can help activate them.   Your rooks are generally strong when placed on open files or in the center. Prioritize the development of knights and bishops over rooks. This strategy comes from the fact that moving knights and bishops enables castling and activation of your rooks, but you don't get the same benefits from early rook development. }
