1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5
{ The Ruy Lopez! A major opening in chess. White develops the bishop, targets your knight, and gets ready to castle. }
3... Nf6
{ You stick to the principles and develop your knight first. This is known as the Berlin Defense. I suggest playing the Berlin in a modern and aggressive way.  Moving your pawn to the center with  3...d5?  wouldn't work for the usual reason: after  4.exd5  Qxd5  , White gains a tempo on the queen with  5.Nc3  . Another problem with  3...d5?  is that your knight is pinned, so  4.Nxe5  would lose a pawn.   3...a6  is the Spanish opening and an alternative move. }
4. Nc3 { The four knights Ruy Lopez! } 4... Bc5
{ You develop the bishop as usual. } 5. O-O O-O { You castle as well! } 6. Nxe5
{ White can go for the same trick one move later. } 6... Nxe5 7. d4 Bd6 8. f4
{ 8.fxe5  Bxe5  is not dangerous for you. } 8... Nc6
{ You stick to the same plan. } 9. e5 Bb4
{ Again, you opt for the same solution as before. } 10. exf6 Qxf6 11. a3
{ You must capture when the knight is not pinned. } 11... Bxc3
{ You capture now as the knight is not pinned!  After  11...Ba5  White can play  12.Nd5  now and after  12...Qxd4+  13.Be3  Qxd1  14.Raxd1  leaves you in a bad situation as b4 is coming, and you will lose the c7-pawn  The direct @@StartFEN@@r1b2rk1/pppp1ppp/2n2q2/1B6/1b1P1P2/2N5/PPP3PP/R1BQ1RK1 w - - 0 11@@EndFEN@@  11.Nd5  didn't give this problem since there after  11...Qxd4  12.Be3  Qxd1  13.Raxd1  , you can still hold on to the c7-pawn with  13...Bd6 }
12. bxc3 a6
{ An important move!  After  12...d5?  13.f5  , you are in trouble. This move blocks your bishop, and White's dark-squared bishop will become powerful. }
13. Be2
{ White drops the bishop back and avoids the tactic. The bishop is misplaced here and blocks the queen. This makes the plan to play f5 less dangerous because White is unable to follow it up with a quick Qh5 and Bg5 attack.  
Note that  13.Bd3  allows a tactic with  13...Nxd4  since after  14.cxd4  Qxd4+  forks the king and rook }
13... b5 { You want to activate your dark-squared bishop quickly. } *

