{ Black eliminates the knight to win the e4-pawn. } 12. bxc3 Nxe4 13. Qh5
{ You move your queen to develop and target the h6 pawn, putting Black in significant danger. }
13... Kg7 { The most popular move, but this is losing for Black. } 14. Bxe4
{ You eliminate the defender. } 14... Rxe4 15. f4
{ You open the f-file for the rook. } 15... g4 16. Bf2
{ You will play Rae1 next and trade Black's only defender. After that, Black's king will be helpless and Bd4 will start a devastating attack. }
