16... Bxf5 17. Bxf5
{ Black has a broken pawn structure, and you have a safer king. The attacking plan you want to go for is Rd1,Rd4,Rg4+, Rb1,b4,Rb3 and you want to attack the king with both your rooks. White runs no risk in this endgame and can go after Black's king. }
