13. Bxe7 { It's time to capture the bishop and attack back. } 13... Nxg3
{ Capturing the queen would be a big mistake for Black. } 14. Bxd8 Nxf1 15. Bg5
{ And Black's knight is trapped, which means you will get an endgame with two pieces for the rook. }
15... h6 16. Bc1
{ The fastest way to win the knight.  16.Bf4  is also possible, but after  16...g5  you still have to play  17.Bc1 }
16... Nxh2 17. Kxh2
{ With two pieces for a rook in the endgame, you have a dominating advantage. Typically, you can attack every Black pawn one more time. }
