Qxg6+ Bg7 18. f5 { You trap the light-squared bishop. } 18... Nxe5
{ Black can exchange the knights to free the f7-square. } 19. dxe5 Bf7 20. Qxg4
{ You keep the dark-squared bishop pinned and threaten f6 } 20... Rxe5 21. f6
{ You are threatening Qxg7# } 21... Qf8 22. Bh6
{ You are threatening Bxg7 and Black is struggling to stay alive here. } *

