{ Now, the obvious move of grabbing back the bishop would be a mistake.   16...Nc4  is the best move for Black, but good luck to your opponent figuring that out. The point is that now, after  17.Qxc4  Nxh5  , you won't be able to capture the b7-pawn. }
17. dxe5
{ Black's knight is now misplaced, and Black can't win the e5-pawn because the b7-pawn is also hanging. }
