17... e5
{ Pushing the pawn forward would look to me like the most logical thing to do! }
18. h4
{ You are crushing Black, as h5 is coming next. Also, your queen can go to b3 to harass the king. Black can't play  18...h5  themselves, as you will go for  19.Nd5  followed by Ne7+ and Rhg1 }
