17. gxh5 exf2+ 18. Rxf2 Rxf2 19. Kxf2 Be6
{ You develop and get ready for ...Rf8+ } 20. Ba3
{ White wants to exchange queens and go to the endgame. } 20... Rf8+
{ You give a check before trading the queen, but trading first is also fine.   20...Qxd1  21.Bxd1  Rf8+  will lead to the same position. }
