{ With the bishop pair for White, this endgame may look unpleasant, but I found a way to solve all issues. You push the pawn forward, and White is more or less forced to take it, or you will continue with ...e3, and then you either destroy all White's pawn structure, or you have ...Rf2 with an entry square for the rook. }
