{ In this position, the plan is always to get the knight to d4 slowly. Depending on White's play, there are different ways to get there. ...Nd6-Nb5-Nd4 would be the fastest if allowed. ...Nd6-b6-Nb7-Bf7-Nd8-Ne6-Nd4 is a slower possibility. ...c5 and a trade ... Ne7-Nc6-Nd4 would also be a way. }
