15. Bd3 { This would threaten mate. } 15... g6 16. Qxe8
{ White has to bail out to win the pawn back. } 16... Bxd5
{ You capture the knight.   16...Qxe8  is also possible, but White will immediately win your queen back with  17.Nf6+  , and you will get a balanced endgame after  17...Kg7  18.Nxe8  Rxe8  19.Bxc7 }
