{ White adds the knight as an attacker! } 12... d5
{ An important move supporting your knight and activating your bishop.  After  12...Bxc3?  13.Qh5+  Ke7  14.bxc3  the position is falling apart, White threatens Bg5+ to win the queen, as well as Qxf5. }
13. Nxd5 { Wins a pawn for White! } 13... Qxd5 14. Qxf6
