8. dxe5 Nb7 { You can use the b7-square to safeguard your knight. } 9. Nd4
{ White prepares for Rd1 followed by Nxc6 } 9... O-O
{ Castling provides an escape square for the queen. } 10. Rd1 Qe8 11. Nf5
