16... Re8+ { You go after the king. } 17. Be3 Qc5 18. Qxc5 Bxc5
{ Attacking the pinned bishop! } 19. bxc3
{ White is forced to ruin their pawn structure as  19.Rxc3  runs into the pin with  19...Bb4 }
