{ This defends against the Ra3 idea. Important not to be great with  20...Rxe3+  because after  21.Kf2  Re8  , you just won an ugly pawn but  22.Ra3  comes, and after  22...Bc8  23.Rxa7  , you lost the important a-pawn and are about to lose the c7-pawn as well. }
21. Ra3 Rxe3+ { Before defending you first grab a pawn. } 22. Kf2 Re6
{ Everything is under control! You want to bring your last rook into the attack with ...h5-...Rh6-Rhf6+. }
