8... Nxd5 9. Bxd5 c6 { You chase the bishop away to trade it. } 10. Bb3 Nxb3
{ You catch White's light-squared bishop. } 11. axb3 a5
{ You can start gaining space on the queenside and continue with ...b5-...a4. }
