{ White blocks the bishop diagonal and wants to capture on c4 next. It's time to continue the energetic play. }
10... Bxe3 { You will get an exchange and a couple of pawns for the piece. }
11. fxe3 Nxe3 { White's rook can't escape to a safe square. } 12. Rf1 Nxf1 13.
Kxf1 O-O
{ There is no good way to hold on to the c4-pawn since after  13...Na5?  14.Ne5  White will win the pawn either way. }
14. Nxc4 f6
{ Black aims to get a strong pawn structure in the center with ... e5 and also activate the rook with ...Rd8 and ...Rb8 }
