{ White goes for a counterattack and chases back your bishop. } 14... Be7
{ You slide the bishop back and start eyeing White's queen. } 15. Ba6
{ It's always good to see that White's bishop leaves the powerful diagonal in the Catalan. }
15... O-O
{ You castle! White should now get worried about ...Nd5 coming next, as the queen is poorly placed.   15...Nd5?  didn't work yet since after  16.Qg4  White attacks your g7-pawn. }
