7... Rxb8 8. Qd4 e6 { You threaten to capture the pawn again with ...Bxc5 } 9.
b4 { This was White's idea but the pawns will still stay weak. } 9... Qd8
{ Next move ...b6 is coming and White's pawn structure is about to collapse. With the bishop pair you are in great shape here. }
