7. a3 { White aims to play b4 and get a strong structure. } 7... Qxc5
{ You capture the pawn before White can defend it. } 8. Nge2 e6
{ You want to wait to develop your knight after you are castled because after  9.Nd4  Nc6  10.Ndb5  will be played and White again aims for the typical fork in the Jobava London. }
9. Nd4 Be7 { You develop and get ready to castle. } 10. Ndb5 Bxb5
