12. Nef4 { White supports the knight! } 12... Bb4+
{ It's time to start developing fast! } 13. c3 Rhe8
{ Active play! Since White's king is still on the e-file, it would be way too dangerous for White to capture your bishop now.   14.cxb4  Bxd5  clears the e-file and after  15.Qxd5  Nc3+  wins the queen with the discovered attack. }
14. O-O { White castles to get out of the attack! } 14... Bxd5
{ It's time to capture everything. } 15. Nxd5 Qxd5 16. Qxd5 Rxd5 17. cxb4
{ Capturing the bishop would be a mistake for White. } 17... Nxb4
{ Black is a pawn up, and the bishop pair doesn't pose any danger as White's light-squared bishop is blocked. }
